T02D2108:146a-29: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gsung khyod la'o //
T02D2108:146a-30: rdo rje las rab rdo rje bka' //
T02D2108:146a-31: las kyi rdo rje kun rab 'gro //
T02D2108:146a-32: rdo rje nges pa rgya che ba //
T02D2108:146a-33: phyag 'tshal rdo rje rgya gram la'o //
T02D2108:146a-34: rdo rje sku ni brtan pa che //
T02D2108:146a-35: rdo rje go cha sra ba ste //
T02D2108:146a-36: brtson 'grus mchog ste dka' thub che //
T02D2108:146a-38: rdo rje gnod sbyin thabs chen po //
T02D2108:146a-39: rdo rje mche ba gtsigs pa che //
T02D2108:146a-40: bdud 'joms rdo rje mi zad pa //
T02D2108:146a-41: phyag 'tshal rdo rje drag po la //
T02D2108:146a-42: rdo rje mtshams sbyor rab tu 'dud //
T02D2108:146a-43: rdo rje bcings pa rab grol cing //
T02D2108:146a-44: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gnyis med la'o //
T02D2108:146a-45: lhag chad yi ge brgya pas bshags /
T02D2108:146a-47: bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis //
T02D2108:146a-48: 'gro ba ma lus 'den par shog /'jam dpal gyi
T02D2108:146a-49: sgrub thabs zhi ba 'od kyi rim pa zhes bya
T02D2108:146a-51: / sdom pa bzang po'i thugs dam /
